if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
! ============================================================================== ! ! ============================================================================== ! 3D model ! ==============================================================================
pen gs_cont_pen
if GLOB_CONTEXT > 20 and GLOB_CONTEXT < 40 then material box_mat
prism_ 4, zzyzx, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, b, 15, 0, b, 15 else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then cutplane 1, 1, 0, 1 B = B - 0.01
! Detailed kY = A / 24 !button size X kX = B / 8.25 !button size y r = 54.5 * ZZYZX !radius of keyboard curve alpha = (180 * B) / (PI * r) !angle of keyboard curve h = 54.5 * (ZZYZX) * (1 - cos(alpha)) !support leg height
rotz -90 roty alpha/2 addx -B
RESOL 16
bprism_ box_mat, box_mat, box_mat, 5, ZZYZX - h, r, 0, 0, 13, B, 0, 15, B, A, 15, 0, A, 8, 0, 0, -1
ADDZ ZZYZX - h bprism_ cover_mat, cover_mat, cover_mat, 54, 0.003, r + ZZYZX - h, 0, 0.005, 13, B, 0.005, 15, B, A - 0.005, 15, 0, A - 0.005, 8, 0, 0.005, -1, !end of contour
3 * kX, 0.5 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 0.5 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 15.5 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 15.5 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 0.5 * kY, -1, !end of letter pad
3 * kX, 16 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 19 * kY, 15, 5 * kX, 19 * kY, 15, 5 * kX, 16 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 16 * kY, -1, !end of positioning pad
3 * kX, 19.5 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 19.5 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 23.5 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 23.5 * kY, 15, 3 * kX, 19.5 * kY, -1, !end of num pad
1.5 * kX, 0.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 0.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 1.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 1.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 0.5 * kY, -1, !end of esc button
1.5 * kX, 2.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 2.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 6.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 6.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 2.5 * kY, -1, !end of F1-F4
1.5 * kX, 7 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 7 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 11 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 11 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 7 * kY, -1, !end of F5-F8
1.5 * kX, 11.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 11.5 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 15.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 15.5 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 11.5 * kY, -1, !end of F9-F12
1.5 * kX, 16 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 16 * kY, 15, 2.5 * kX, 19 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 19 * kY, 15, 1.5 * kX, 16 * kY, -1, !end of P-S-P buttons
7 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 16 * kY, 15, 8 * kX, 19 * kY, 15, 7 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY, 15, 7 * kX - 0.002, 18 * kY + 0.002, 15, 6 * kX, 18 * kY + 0.002, 15, 6 * kX, 17 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX - 0.002, 17 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY, -1 !end of arrows DEL 1 c = 0.01
cprism_ box_mat, box_mat, box_mat, !curved part 1 9, ZZYZX - h, 0, 0, 8, 0, A, 79, 0, A-c, 900, -c, A-c, 3079, -c, A-c, 79, -c, c, 79, c, 90, 2079, 0, 0, 79, 0, 0, -1
ADDZ ZZYZX - h
c = 0.005 cprism_ cover_mat, cover_mat, cover_mat, !curved part 2
9, 0.003, 0, 0.005, 8, 0, A - 0.005, 79, 0, A - 0.005 - c, 900, -c, A - c - 0.005, 3079, -c, A - c - 0.005, 79, -c, c + 0.005, 79, c, 90, 2079, 0, 0.005, 79, 0, 0.005, -1
DEL 1
ADDZ ZZYZX - h
r = 54.5 * ZZYZX
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "letterkeysmat") keyb_side_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "antracite") else keyb_side_mat = keyb_mat endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 3 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of letter buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 0.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "poskeysmat") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 3 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 5 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 5 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of positioning pad buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 16 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "numpadmat") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 23.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 23.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of num pad buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 19.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "escmat") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 1.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 1.5 * kY- 0.002 , 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of esc button
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 0.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "functionmat1") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 2.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 2.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 6.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 6.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 2.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of F1-F4
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 2.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "functionmat5") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 7 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 7 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 11 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 11 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 7 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of F5-F8
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 7 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "functionmat9") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 11.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 11.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 11.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of F9-F12
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 11.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "pspmat") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of P-S-P buttons
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 16 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "arrowsmat") endif
bprism_ keyb_side_mat, keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, 9, 0.006, r + ZZYZX - h, 7 * kX , 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX , 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX , 18 * kY, 15, 6 * kX + 0.002, 18 * kY, 15, 6 * kX + 0.002, 17 * kY, 15, 7 * kX , 17 * kY , 15, 7 * kX , 16 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of arrows
vert1 = 6 vert2 = 16 gosub "vertex" del 1 addz -h cprism_ box_mat, box_mat, box_mat, !support leg 5, h, 0, 3 * kY, 15, 0, 21 * kY, 15, 1 * kX, 21 * kY, 15, 1 * kX, 3 * kY, 15, 0, 3 * kY, -1 DEL 4 cutend else
! simple ROTZ -180 ROTY -90 ADDY -B cprism_ box_mat, box_mat, box_mat, 7, A, 0, 0, 15, ZZYZX - 0.003, 0, 15, (ZZYZX - 0.003) / 2, B, 15, 0, B, 15, (ZZYZX - 0.003) / 2, B / 6, 15, 0, B / 6, 15, 0, 0, -1
ADDX ZZYZX - 0.003 alpha = atn((ZZYZX - 0.003) / 2 / B) ROTZ alpha ROTY 90 ADDX -A C = sqr(B ^ 2 + ((ZZYZX - 0.003) / 2) ^ 2) cprism_ cover_mat, cover_mat, cover_mat, 5, 0.003, 0, 0.003, 15, 0, C-0.003, 15, A, C-0.003, 15, A, 0.003, 15, 0, 0.003, -1
C = sqr((B-0.01) ^ 2 + ((ZZYZX - 0.003) / 2) ^ 2)
ADDZ 0.003 ADDX A ADDY -0.003 ROTZ 90 kY = A / 24 kX = C / 8.25
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "letterkeysmat") keyb_side_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "antracite") else keyb_side_mat = keyb_mat endif
cprism_ keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.003, 3 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 15.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of letter buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 0.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "poskeysmat") endif
cprism_ keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.003, 3 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 5 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 5 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of positioning pad buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 16 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "numpadmat") endif
cprism_ keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.003, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 23.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 23.5 * kY - 0.002, 15, 3 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of num pad buttons
vert1 = 3 vert2 = 19.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "blankbuttonmat") endif
cprism_ keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, keyb_side_mat, 5, 0.003, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY - 0.004 , 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 19.5 * kY - 0.004 , 15, 2.5 * kX - 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 0.5 * kY + 0.002, 15, 1.5 * kX + 0.002, 19.5 * kY - 0.004 , -1 !end of upper buttons
vert1 = 1.5 vert2 = 0.5 gosub "vertex"
if bButtonText then keyb_mat = IND(MATERIAL, "arrowsmat") endif
cprism_ keyb_mat, keyb_side_mat, keyb_side_mat, 9, 0.003, 7 * kX , 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 16 * kY + 0.002, 15, 8 * kX - 0.002, 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX , 19 * kY - 0.002, 15, 7 * kX , 18 * kY, 15, 6 * kX + 0.002, 18 * kY, 15, 6 * kX + 0.002, 17 * kY, 15, 7 * kX , 17 * kY , 15, 7 * kX , 16 * kY + 0.002, -1 !end of arrows
vert1 = 6 vert2 = 16 gosub "vertex"
DEL 11
endif
endif
! ====================================================================== end ! ======================================================================
"vertex":
base vert vert1 * kX + 0.002, vert2 * kY + 0.002, 0 vert vert1 * kX + 0.002, vert2 * kY + 0.002+1, 0 vert vert1 * kX + 0.002-1, vert2 * kY + 0.002, 0 vert vert1 * kX + 0.002, vert2 * kY + 0.002, 1 coor 2 + 256, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
kY = A / 24 !button size X kX = (B-0.01) / 8.25 !button size y
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type poly2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, B, 1, A, B, 1, A, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, B, -1
ADD2 0.5 * kY, 0.25 * kX
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! letter pad ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
rect2 0, 0, 15 * kY, 5 * kX
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then ADD2 kY, 4 * kX ! 1st row nButtons = 13 gosub "oneRow" DEL 1
line2 0, 4 * kX, 15 * kY, 4 * kX ! 2nd row
ADD2 1.5 * kY, 3 * kX nButtons = 13 gosub "oneRow" DEL 1
line2 0, 3 * kX, 13.75 * kY, 3 * kX ! 3rd row
ADD2 1.75 * kY, 2 * kX nButtons = 13 gosub "oneRow" DEL 1
line2 0, 2 * kX, 15 * kY, 2 * kX ! 4th row
ADD2 1.25 * kY, kX nButtons = 12 gosub "oneRow" DEL 1
line2 0, kX, 15 * kY, kX ! 5th row
ADD2 1.75 * kY, 0 for i = 1 to 3 line2 0, 0, 0 * kY, kX ADD2 1.125 * kY, 0 next i DEL 4 ADD2 9.5 * kY, 0 for i = 1 to 4 line2 0, 0, 0, kX ADD2 1.25 * kY, 0 next i DEL 5 endif
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! positioning pad ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADD2 15.5 * kY, 3 * kX rect2 0, 0, 3 * kY, 2 * kX if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then for i = 1 to 2 line2 kY, 0, kY, 2 * kX ADD2 kY, 0 next i DEL 2 line2 0, kX, 3 * kY, kX endif
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! numpad ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADD2 3.5 * kY, -3 * kx rect2 0, 0, 4 * kY, 5 * kX if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then for i = 1 to 2 line2 0, kX, 3 * kY, kX ADD2 0, 2 * kX next i DEL 2 for i = 1 to 2 line2 0, 2 * kX, 4 * kY, 2 *kX ADD2 0, 2 * kX next i DEL 2 ADD2 kY, 0 for i = 1 to 2 line2 kY, 0, kY, 5 * kX ADD2 kY, 0 next i DEL 3 line2 kY, kX, kY, 5 * kX endif
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! arrows ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADD2 -3.5 * kY, 0 poly2_B 9, 1, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, 0, kX, 1, kY, kX, 1, kY, 2 * kX, 1, 2 * kY, 2 * kX, 1, 2 * kY, kX, 1, 3 * kY, kX, 1, 3 * kY, 0, 1, 0, 0, -1
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then line2 kY, 0, kY, kX line2 2 * kY, 0, 2 * kY, kX line2 kY, kX, 2 * kY, kX endif
DEL 4
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! upper row buttons ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ADD2 0.5 * kY, 5.75 * kX rect2 0, 0, kY, kX ADD2 2 * kY, 0 for i = 1 to 3 rect2 0, 0, 4* kY, kX if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then for j = 1 to 3 line2 kY, 0, kY, kX ADD2 kY, 0 next j DEL 3 endif ADD2 4.5 * kY, 0 next i
rect2 0, 0, 3* kY, kX if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then for i = 1 to 2 line2 kY, 0, kY, kX ADD2 kY, 0 next i del 2 endif
del 5
end
"oneRow": for i = 1 to nButtons line2 0, 0, 0, kX ADD2 kY, 0 next i del nButtons return
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`, `Простой`, `Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1, 2 lock "A", "B", "ZZYZX" values "gs_detlevel_2D" `Простой`,`Детальный` values "gs_detlevel_2D_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 else if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 else parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 endif endif else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` else parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` endif endif endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_2D" then if gs_detlevel_2D = `Простой` then parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 else parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 endif else if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_2D = `Простой` else parameters gs_detlevel_2D = `Детальный` endif endif
if bButtonText then lock "keyb_mat" hideparameter "keyb_mat" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_shadow"
IF gs_cont_pen<=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=10 IF gs_fill_pen<=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
